                    <p class="company-name">VELO.AI, INC.</p>
                    <a href={base_url("/research-areas/artificial-intelligence/transportation-planning-design/projects/infrastructure-interventions-near-miss")} class="btn btn-sm btn-primary">
                      Learn More
